    • Method Detail

      • createFreshModel

        public void createFreshModel()
        This method fills the class variables player1Team, player2Team and model with six characters for each team and an empty field. This model can then be used for tests and can easily be reset by calling this method again. This method assumes, that the files "asgard.json", "marvelhero.json" and "matchconfig_1.json" are located in the root directory of this project.
